<dec f='Modules/Image/Contrib/TurboJpeg/turbojpeg.h' l='933' type='unsigned long tjBufSizeYUV2(int width, int pad, int height, int subsamp)'/>
<doc f='Modules/Image/Contrib/TurboJpeg/turbojpeg.h' l='916'>/**
 * The size of the buffer (in bytes) required to hold a YUV planar image with
 * the given parameters.
 *
 * @param width width (in pixels) of the image
 *
 * @param pad the width of each line in each plane of the image is padded to
 * the nearest multiple of this number of bytes (must be a power of 2.)
 *
 * @param height height (in pixels) of the image
 *
 * @param subsamp level of chrominance subsampling in the image (see
 * @ref TJSAMP &quot;Chrominance subsampling options&quot;.)
 *
 * @return the size of the buffer (in bytes) required to hold the image, or
 * -1 if the arguments are out of bounds.
 */</doc>
